Title: 从左向右方向
Describe: None
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
None

[Description]
默认从上往下构建图示。

[UML]
@startuml
'default
top to bottom direction
user1 --> (Usecase 1)
user2 --> (Usecase 2)

@enduml
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
None

[Description]
你可以用 `left to right direction` 命令改变图示方向。

[UML]
@startuml

left to right direction
user1 --> (Usecase 1)
user2 --> (Usecase 2)

@enduml
------------------------------------------------------------
